### 2. Scalability Patterns
Identify the scalability patterns most relevant to the stated traffic profile. Consider: auto-scaling policies, CQRS, read replicas, queue-based load leveling, sharding, and horizontal vs. vertical scaling trade-offs.

### 3. Caching Strategy
